snippet.title: Homeseek - Official Release Date Trailer | Future Games Show 2023
snippet.description: Traptics revealed a July release date for Homeseek, a post-apocalyptic survival strategy game set on a dystopian resource-strapped Earth at the beginning of the next century where water has become the new gold. Homeseek comes to PC July 20, 2023.
